ute so that Bayesian analysis becomes a\ntool in the toolkit of researchers, and they understand by experience its\nadvantages and limitations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jan 2016 21:38:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-01"}
